d still trust `cwd` fields inside\n+the JSONL records over decoding the directory name. The directory encoding is\n+lossy and should only narrow the search.\n+\n+Discovery should prefer recent modified files, validate transcript `cwd` against\n+the selected GitButler worktree, and auto-select only when exactly one plausible\n+candidate remains.\n+\n ## Freshness\n*** End Patch\n","source_record":{"timestamp":"2026-05-07T18:31:38.259Z","type":"response_item","payload":{"type":"custom_tool_call","status":"completed","call_id":"[REDACTED:entropy]","name":"apply_patch"}}}